content.html: Hello! I was one of the editors of the HTML5 specification. I had no idea what I was doing when I started. But I asked for help. I looked things up. I learned from others. I exposed my ignorance because I'm secure enough to handle the dingbats - and I wanted to encourage others.
content.value:
Hello! I was one of the editors of the HTML5 specification. I had no idea what I was doing when I started. But I asked for help. I looked things up. I learned from others. 
I exposed my ignorance because I'm secure enough to handle the dingbats - and I wanted to encourage others.
